## Step 11 — Handoff / Loop Continue

**In AUTO-LOOP MODE:**
- Confirm: browser agent verified at CANVAS_W px (desktop) and 375px (mobile).
- Section marked `[x]` in PROGRESS.md.
- State what section is next and immediately begin Step 0 for it.

**In single-section mode:**
Send one message containing:
- Section name, badge text, visible heading.
- Position in `page.tsx` (what it sits between).
- Assets exported and where saved.
- New tokens added (or "none").
- Local `const` values and why they weren't tokenised.
- Browser agent verification result: desktop CANVAS_W px ✓, mobile 375px ✓.

